{"id": "1377994766045810739", "channel_id": "1377627804044365854", "type": 0, "author_id": "557599119401811978", "author_name": "heikwok", "author_bot": false, "content": "醫生有新易傷虛弱 力量拐", "timestamp": "2025-05-30T12:59:14.130000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1377627804044365854", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "📜卡斯托爾┊喚醒體&命輪介紹；Castor┊Awaker & Wheel of Destiny Introduction", "forum_channel_id": "1355085076500578363", "thread_tags": ["1356827958647586947", "1356828359543226469"]}
{"id": "1377994826686926909", "channel_id": "1377627804044365854", "type": 0, "author_id": "422799061133950978", "author_name": "ernest_heart", "author_bot": false, "content": "肯定是帶菲的", "timestamp": "2025-05-30T12:59:28.588000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1377627804044365854", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "📜卡斯托爾┊喚醒體&命輪介紹；Castor┊Awaker & Wheel of Destiny Introduction", "forum_channel_id": "1355085076500578363", "thread_tags": ["1356827958647586947", "1356828359543226469"]}
{"id": "1377994877886926882", "channel_id": "1377627804044365854", "type": 0, "author_id": "422799061133950978", "author_name": "ernest_heart", "author_bot": false, "content": "覺醒無敵自動固傷", "timestamp": "2025-05-30T12:59:40.795000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1377627804044365854", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "📜卡斯托爾┊喚醒體&命輪介紹；Castor┊Awaker & Wheel of Destiny Introduction", "forum_channel_id": "1355085076500578363", "thread_tags": ["1356827958647586947", "1356828359543226469"]}
{"id": "1377997271907434576", "channel_id": "1377627804044365854", "type": 19, "author_id": "557599119401811978", "author_name": "heikwok", "author_bot": false, "content": "然後看3費那個暴傷拐效果能不能疊，這樣囤4~5張一次打出，隊友都能吃到鳥本體持有的60%~75%暴傷拐了\n或者隊友帶一張米拉專左腳踩右腳", "timestamp": "2025-05-30T13:09:11.574000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1368964220506472558"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1377994463611457637", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1377627804044365854", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "📜卡斯托爾┊喚醒體&命輪介紹；Castor┊Awaker & Wheel of Destiny Introduction", "forum_channel_id": "1355085076500578363", "thread_tags": ["1356827958647586947", "1356828359543226469"]}
{"id": "1378000536023994420", "channel_id": "1377627804044365854", "type": 19, "author_id": "1368964220506472558", "author_name": "chunjuyi", "author_bot": false, "content": "如果鸟200多爆伤，四五张三费拐给其他队友也就是100多爆伤，假设队友有400爆伤再用米粒专拐回来给鸟提供60爆伤。再算上鼠鼠给鸟提供的爆伤，鸟应该可以多200爆伤。\n\n唔，鼠鼠和医生，在伤害方面，就是考虑200爆伤和45独立增伤哪个更好了。", "timestamp": "2025-05-30T13:22:09.800000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["557599119401811978"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1377997271907434576", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1377627804044365854", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "📜卡斯托爾┊喚醒體&命輪介紹；Castor┊Awaker & Wheel of Destiny Introduction", "forum_channel_id": "1355085076500578363", "thread_tags": ["1356827958647586947", "1356828359543226469"]}
{"id": "1378001148098773082", "channel_id": "1377627804044365854", "type": 0, "author_id": "1368964220506472558", "author_name": "chunjuyi", "author_bot": false, "content": "鉴于卡斯本身的高爆伤数值，还有医生还能提供大量银钥，感觉还是医生更好一点，不过卡斯和医生抢超距😋", "timestamp": "2025-05-30T13:24:35.730000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1377627804044365854", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "📜卡斯托爾┊喚醒體&命輪介紹；Castor┊Awaker & Wheel of Destiny Introduction", "forum_channel_id": "1355085076500578363", "thread_tags": ["1356827958647586947", "1356828359543226469"]}
{"id": "1378001512864677888", "channel_id": "1377627804044365854", "type": 0, "author_id": "1368964220506472558", "author_name": "chunjuyi", "author_bot": false, "content": "这点其实好像也没太大关系，反正医生觉醒不用第一张出也能生效，就是少个超距的力量而已", "timestamp": "2025-05-30T13:26:02.697000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1377627804044365854", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "📜卡斯托爾┊喚醒體&命輪介紹；Castor┊Awaker & Wheel of Destiny Introduction", "forum_channel_id": "1355085076500578363", "thread_tags": ["1356827958647586947", "1356828359543226469"]}
{"id": "1378001789458317334", "channel_id": "1377627804044365854", "type": 0, "author_id": "557599119401811978", "author_name": "heikwok", "author_bot": false, "content": "只能讓醫生超限拿力量或者卡斯回狂夠快也不需用倚賴超距了", "timestamp": "2025-05-30T13:27:08.642000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1377627804044365854", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "📜卡斯托爾┊喚醒體&命輪介紹；Castor┊Awaker & Wheel of Destiny Introduction", "forum_channel_id": "1355085076500578363", "thread_tags": ["1356827958647586947", "1356828359543226469"]}
{"id": "1378002052705157241", "channel_id": "1377627804044365854", "type": 0, "author_id": "557599119401811978", "author_name": "heikwok", "author_bot": false, "content": "畢竟有羊媽詩人", "timestamp": "2025-05-30T13:28:11.405000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1377627804044365854", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "📜卡斯托爾┊喚醒體&命輪介紹；Castor┊Awaker & Wheel of Destiny Introduction", "forum_channel_id": "1355085076500578363", "thread_tags": ["1356827958647586947", "1356828359543226469"]}
{"id": "1378002293395423273", "channel_id": "1377627804044365854", "type": 0, "author_id": "557599119401811978", "author_name": "heikwok", "author_bot": false, "content": "而且只有羊媽一隻血肉胚胎估計還會有溢出", "timestamp": "2025-05-30T13:29:08.790000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1377627804044365854", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "📜卡斯托爾┊喚醒體&命輪介紹；Castor┊Awaker & Wheel of Destiny Introduction", "forum_channel_id": "1355085076500578363", "thread_tags": ["1356827958647586947", "1356828359543226469"]}
{"id": "1378035520642486343", "channel_id": "1377627804044365854", "type": 19, "author_id": "1368964220506472558", "author_name": "chunjuyi", "author_bot": false, "content": "深潜的话，感觉温前面给鸟产黑羽，后面给羊妈复制鸟3费，这样会不会更好一点🤔", "timestamp": "2025-05-30T15:41:10.783000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["557599119401811978"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1377994707745112064", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1377627804044365854", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "📜卡斯托爾┊喚醒體&命輪介紹；Castor┊Awaker & Wheel of Destiny Introduction", "forum_channel_id": "1355085076500578363", "thread_tags": ["1356827958647586947", "1356828359543226469"]}
{"id": "1378036682879668446", "channel_id": "1377627804044365854", "type": 19, "author_id": "557599119401811978", "author_name": "heikwok", "author_bot": false, "content": "差不多吧，不然溫帶普朵專+SR那張群體回5狂之類的順帶拉全隊也行", "timestamp": "2025-05-30T15:45:47.882000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1368964220506472558"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1378035520642486343", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1377627804044365854", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "📜卡斯托爾┊喚醒體&命輪介紹；Castor┊Awaker & Wheel of Destiny Introduction", "forum_channel_id": "1355085076500578363", "thread_tags": ["1356827958647586947", "1356828359543226469"]}
{"id": "1378036855995367636", "channel_id": "1377627804044365854", "type": 0, "author_id": "557599119401811978", "author_name": "heikwok", "author_bot": false, "content": "但可能羊媽要放生機充銀鑰了", "timestamp": "2025-05-30T15:46:29.156000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1377627804044365854", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "📜卡斯托爾┊喚醒體&命輪介紹；Castor┊Awaker & Wheel of Destiny Introduction", "forum_channel_id": "1355085076500578363", "thread_tags": ["1356827958647586947", "1356828359543226469"]}
{"id": "1378037267272175647", "channel_id": "1377627804044365854", "type": 0, "author_id": "557599119401811978", "author_name": "heikwok", "author_bot": false, "content": "用醫生的話銀鑰兩張可以給她，然後羊媽帶熔朵專拿狂氣返還，整體狂氣銀鑰的回轉應該會更好", "timestamp": "2025-05-30T15:48:07.212000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1377627804044365854", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "📜卡斯托爾┊喚醒體&命輪介紹；Castor┊Awaker & Wheel of Destiny Introduction", "forum_channel_id": "1355085076500578363", "thread_tags": ["1356827958647586947", "1356828359543226469"]}
{"id": "1378039195783925861", "channel_id": "1377627804044365854", "type": 0, "author_id": "1368964220506472558", "author_name": "chunjuyi", "author_bot": false, "content": "是的，带医生回转更好，带温的话得考虑额外的充气（凹狂气造物<:cute1:1356053053568192717> ）。不过我想着如果鸟每回合能稳定双大的话，鸟每回合多10%终伤<:cute1:1356053053568192717> 再算上爆发回合多复制的两张三费，可能最终伤害可以超过带医生。", "timestamp": "2025-05-30T15:55:47.005000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-05-30T15:57:02.216000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1377627804044365854", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "📜卡斯托爾┊喚醒體&命輪介紹；Castor┊Awaker & Wheel of Destiny Introduction", "forum_channel_id": "1355085076500578363", "thread_tags": ["1356827958647586947", "1356828359543226469"]}
